  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00739', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作者在服務過程中碰到有毒癮的青少年仍持續吸毒，卻欺騙社會工作者已經找到工作且再也沒有 吸毒；但在一次個案會談中社會工作者發現案主的欺騙，一氣之下當場以不當言語辱罵案主。該社會工 作者違反下列那一個專業價值？', '["保密", "非批判的態度", "案主自決", "充權"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00740', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '成年未婚懷孕婦女對於「生下孩子」、「墮胎」、「出養」等決策猶豫不決。社會工作者應該如何協助 案主進行決策？', '["找出胎兒之父親，尊重其意見", "透過家族會議，進行決策", "請案主參酌同儕意見，進行決策", "協助案主釐清意見，充權案主解決問題的能量"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 10, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00741', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-111-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '當社會工作者發現同事應服務對象生前之要求，在其過世後不告知家人便代為處理喪事。下列那一項作 法不符合專業倫理？', '["與該位同事討論與進行補救", "協助該位同事遮掩事件，以免傷害同儕關係與機構聲譽", "尋求機構主管的協助與介入", "透過社會工作師公會或相關專業組織採取介入行動"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:11+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2fbac3fb0314", "answer_pdf_sha1": "ec43feddf564", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 11, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
